#include<iostream>
#include<math.h>
using namespace std;
bool isSq(int n){
    int x=sqrt(n);
    return x*x==n;
}
int main(){
    int t;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--){
        int n;
        cin>>n;
        if(isSq(5*pow(n,2)+4)||isSq(5*pow(n,2)-4))
            cout<<"is fibo"<<endl;
        else
            cout<<"not fibo"<<endl;
    }
}
